Effective Date: 06/04/2025

WhimsyWall ("we", "our", or "us") provides high-quality wallpapers inspired by the world of Ghibli through our mobile application ("the App"). This Privacy Policy explains how your information is collected, used, and shared.

1. Information We Collect
We do not collect personally identifiable information. However, we use third-party services such as Firebase and Unity Ads which may collect anonymized usage data for analytics and ad delivery.

2. Advertising
We use Unity Ads to serve ads. Unity may collect device information, advertising IDs, and usage patterns to deliver relevant ads. You can review Unity’s privacy policy here: https://unity.com/legal/privacy-policy

3. Analytics
We use Firebase Analytics to understand how users interact with the app. This helps us improve user experience. You can review Google’s privacy policy here: https://policies.google.com/privacy

4. Permissions
The App may request access to storage in order to download and save wallpapers to your device. This is strictly used for that functionality.

5. Data Retention
We do not retain any personal information on our servers.

6. Changes
We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Continued use of the app implies consent to the updated policy.

7. Contact
For any questions, please contact: [your email address]
